Synopsis:
   ban [<channel> <pattern> <nick>] 

Description:
   BAN will attempt to ban either a nick or a anyone matching the specified
   pattern. If the nick is not found in the channel, the server will be
   queryed for a match.

Examples:
   /ban fudd
   /ban #warez1 fizzle_b
   /ban #bitchx *idt*

